<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4894326>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 8. Areca riparia. A. Stem, leaf and inflorescence. B. Detail of rachilla showing staminate and pistillate flowers in bud. C. Staminate flower in section. D. Pistillate flower. E, F. Fruit whole and in section. Scale bar: A = 4 cm; B = 7 mm; C = 1 mm; D = 3 mm; E, F = 1 cm. All from Evans 174. Drawn by Lucy T. Smith." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4894326/files/figure.png" .

